Package: ncdf4helpers
Title: Helpers to easily read from and write NetCDF files
Description: This package wraps `ncdf4` functions and provide interfaces to easily read arrays from NetCDF files or write full data.frames as a NetCDF file.
Version: 0.2
Author: Jean-Olivier Irisson
Maintainer: Jean-Olivier Irisson <irisson@normalesup.org>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
License: GPL-3
LazyData: true
Depends:
    ncdf4
Imports:
    graphics,
    plyr,
    reshape2
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
